      <description>&lt;p&gt;Quick Description: A weather station connected to IoT cloud, updateding cloud variables.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Description: This is my first project, where I used an ESP-32 Microcontroller to power a DHT-11 sensor and create a weather station connected to the cloud via Arduino&amp;rsquo;s IoT cloud device service. I sought to introduce myself to the connection between hardware and software, and thought that this project would be a good start&lt;/p&gt;</description>
